# === Hermes / user-context-leak guards ===
# The terminal tool's "subdirectory context discovery" can drop
# AGENTS.md, llms.txt, and .agents/ into the working tree of a
# freshly-cloned repo (the user's GLOBAL workflow files). We block
# .agents/ wholesale. AGENTS.md and llms.txt are intentionally
# NOT blocked — this repo has its own AGENTS.md and llms.txt as
# project documentation. To avoid accidentally committing a
# Hermes-injected copy, audit staged files before each commit and
# verify the AGENTS.md / llms.txt content matches the repo's own
# authoring (not the user's ~/.hermes/ templates).
.agents/
